# API Route Patterns

## Response Format

```typescript
// Success
return new Response(JSON.stringify({ data: result }), { status: 200 })

// Error
return new Response(
  JSON.stringify({ error: "Message", code: "ERROR_CODE" }),
  { status: 400 }
)
```

## Authentication

```typescript
import { auth } from "@clerk/nextjs/server"

export async function POST(req: Request) {
  const { userId } = await auth()
  if (!userId) {
    return new Response(JSON.stringify({ error: "Unauthorized" }), { status: 401 })
  }
  // ...
}
```

## Validation

Use Zod schemas with `safeParse`. Return 400 with `code: "VALIDATION_ERROR"` on failure.

## Streaming Responses

Use the `toUIMessageStreamResponse` pattern from AGENTS.md. Always pass `sendReasoning`, `sendSources`, and `onError`.

## Long-Running Routes

```typescript
export const maxDuration = 60  // seconds
```
